N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. tit. 20, ch. XVI, pt. 8193 - Assessor's Reports

State Regulations

Subpart 8193-4 - Assessor's Report For Equalization Purposes And Of Exempt Property For All Assessment Rolls Required To Be Filed On Or After January 1, 1996 (§ 8193-4.1 to 8193-4.5)

Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. tit. 20, ch. XVI, pt. 8193

Statutory authority: Real Property Tax Law, §§ 202[1][k], [l], 214, 575, 842, 1200, 1202, 1220, 1314[2]
State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
